# Results

All results obtained using SolverCUDA from one of the following systems:

1. NVIDIA GeForce RTX 3070, CUDA Toolkit 11.7 on Ubuntu 22.04 LTS, Intel(R) Core(TM) i7-10700K CPU @ 3.80GHz
2. NVIDIA L4, CUDA Toolkit 12.2 on Ubuntu 22.04.2 LTS, Intel(R) Xeon(R) CPU @ 2.20GHz
3. NVIDIA A100-SXM4-40GB, CUDA Toolkit 12.2 on Ubuntu 22.04.2 LTS, Intel(R) Xeon(R) CPU @ 2.20GHz

I only show results for games where I've determined the best starting guess. This takes a long time for larger games, thus the tables are only partially filled.

*Times reported are from the first system unless otherwise marked.* *Raw data is in the .json files in subdirectories here.*
